address stop showing me this for the remainder of my visit rubicon technology inc  semiorg skip to main content     contact us search form search select regions taiwan japan europe korea north america china south east asia members only log in membership market info standards advocacy toggle navigation rubicon technology inc rubicon technology incstreet address  e green st unit abensenvilleilunited statesweb site address httpwwwrubicontechnologycom company description rubicon technology is a leading materials science solutions provider in the research manufacturing marketing and distribution of highquality single crystal sapphire and other advanced technology materials our chicago based crystal growth fabrication polishing and cleaning facilities provide a consistent supply of the highest quality epi ready substrates windows rods rodstock lenses tubes blanks and boules coupled with excellent service rubicon uses the proprietary kyrplus crystal growth method and technology to grow the finest quality largediameter and highdensity single crystal sapphire in all orientations rubicons sapphire products have a lower dislocation density or edge pit density epd higher transmission in the uv range are ultra flat epiready clean uniformly flat and consistent and precise tolerances these qualities make our polished substrates an ideal choice for white blue and hb leds lds optoelectronic telecommunications optical  laser compound semiconductor and semiconductor fabrication applications rubicon also offers quartz cesium iodide germanium magnesium fluoride calcium fluoride lithium fluoride barium fluoride zinc oxide and other exotic materials company id join date feb   address map  primary industry semiconductorprimary product category materialsprimary product sub category wafers rubicon technology inc  sapphire substrates and customized optics select a language english chinese japanese korean home the companysapphire company timeline leadership team careers contact us technologypa