 this template message learn how and when to remove this template message rubicon technology inc type public traded as nasdaq rbcn industry material sapphire substrates founded  website wwwrubicontechnologycomcompany rubicon technology inc is an american company specializing in sapphire crystal growth technology and largediameter sapphire based on traditional kyropoulos technology is marketed as es  the companys markets focus on the led industry and the production of silicon on sapphire sos wafers for integrated circuits rfics as well as on high quality optical and industrial applications contents  history  products  references  external links historyedit in  rubicon technology began its commercial production and was incorporated in  it had growth of a  kg sapphire boule in  in  its polishing capacity was added and it got iso certification in the following year in  rubicon launched  patterned sapphire substrates pss the pss technology was old to its primary customer and continues to provide value today rbcntimelinecompany history ref productsedit rubicon technology is engaged in developing manufacturing and selling monocrystalline sapphire for lightemitting diodes leds radiofrequency integrated circuits rfics optoelectronics and other optical applications rubicon technology successfully produced patterned sapphire substrates pss in a  diameter the company also produced sapphire ingots which were used as raw material for further fabrication referencesedit  company introduction   company descriptation in business wire external linksedit official website retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlerubicontechnologyoldid categories technology companies of the united statescompanies established in companies based in dupage county illinoisbensenville illinoiscompanies listed on nasdaqhidden categories articles with a promotional tone from december all articles with a promotional tonearticles with topics of unclear notability from december all articles with topics of u